CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 29, 1946, pg. 21, reads: "Plan Prom - Putting the finishing touches to plans for the Centre Avenue YMCA's annual graduation prom on Friday, June 28, are members of the committee, left to right: Madeline Swan, Elaine Davis, Harold Keith, Clifford Allen and Dolores Wilson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Four women, including Madeline Sharpe Swan (Foggie) seated on left and Dolores Wilson seated on right, and six men, including Harold Keith seated in center, gathered for meeting in Centre Avenue YMCA
